{"tid":2245410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遼寧女趕不上巴士　衝出馬路頂住　司機踩油「角力」被罰","createTime":"2020-10-16T08:03:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T08:18:24.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2dc4039ccf744d93534c69b3c280510205e460c9","tid":2245410,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201016/393651107747860480189024.jpeg/h--Ks86gYbQMOyhWNMZWU7yx07STbHgoLMrzAyzK8wM?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201016%2F393651107747860480189024.jpeg%2Fh--Ks86gYbQMOyhWNMZWU7yx07STbHgoLMrzAyzK8wM%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=84c7217b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遼寧省瀋陽市一名女子上周六（10日）未能趕上巴士，認為是司機故意不等她，盛怒下竟用肉身擋在巴士前面不讓駛走；巴士司機多次響號警告，甚至一度頂着女子緩慢往前推，但不果，於是報警。事後巴士公司認為，涉事女子雖然做法過激，但司機的處理手法也有錯，因此要求司機賠償對方1000元人民幣（約1150港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0BaZfSxh5sg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0BaZfSxh5sg&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU0YD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=24235dd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0BaZfSxh5sg</a><br />\n網上片段中，身穿藍色外套的女子當日走到馬路中，用身軀擋在巴士正前方阻止駛走；司機多次響號警告，其後甚至緩慢往前推，女子卻繼續無視，還淡定玩手機。目擊者稱，涉事女子認為司機故意不等她，以致未能趕上巴士，因此一路狂追，並趁巴士停在交通燈位時衝前攔截。<br />\n<br />\n瀋陽安運公交公司的發言人事後表示，該名女乘客不應該擋車，但司機明知前方有人仍繼續駛前，其舉動亦有錯誤，因此公司決定將之調職，並要求司機賠償對方1000元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n事件引起爭議，不少網民留言認為涉事女子行為過份，「肆意攔截公共交通工具，都夠治安處罰了，竟然還掙了一千塊錢」、「司機下次遇到這樣的情況直接報警吧，別再衝動行事了，還賠付1000，太倒楣了」；另方面也有意見指司機的確處理不當，「司機再有理也違法了，吊銷執照吧，涉及刑事問題了」、「雖然女子確實不對，但也不能頂着開車吧。我們應該譴責女子，但也希望司機被嚴肅處理，他這脾氣真的可怕」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201016/393608437491044352657841.jpeg/Ec_brsS368lmzHjP4mfAGjgLDpN6taAPWZYqpVmWKqU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201016%2F393608437491044352657841.jpeg%2FEc_brsS368lmzHjP4mfAGjgLDpN6taAPWZYqpVmWKqU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=1104e9a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n身穿藍色外套的女子當日走到馬路中，隔窗不斷指罵司機。（微博影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201016/393608439999369216921634.jpeg/uvXTBZ2YTDs6G0KxwxIajDs-fLrW8mGiHqHq9B6h6vQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201016%2F393608439999369216921634.jpeg%2FuvXTBZ2YTDs6G0KxwxIajDs-fLrW8mGiHqHq9B6h6vQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=732a2154&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n司機多次響號警告示意女子離開。（微博影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201016/393608442411225088543197.jpeg/yysILVbZ-_2J6ERtJU5MH-PRlbcUKWPyyaHdTMmh3Uw?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201016%2F393608442411225088543197.jpeg%2FyysILVbZ-_2J6ERtJU5MH-PRlbcUKWPyyaHdTMmh3Uw%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b2f00032&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴士一度頂着女子往前行駛。（微博影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201016/393608444802109440470812.jpeg/iMqkrlpRBsZ5u0wjK_eN1DS1nLlk1Y5El3d4ZJd3eGQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201016%2F393608444802109440470812.jpeg%2FiMqkrlpRBsZ5u0wjK_eN1DS1nLlk1Y5El3d4ZJd3eGQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ebad9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女子仍不願讓開，反而頂在車前淡定玩手機。（微博影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201016/393612782714490880045968.jpeg/f2Rl7zi2K2pMYVl10EiQDCsWoB7VN84UR4Ne1UeDXtU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201016%2F393612782714490880045968.jpeg%2Ff2Rl7zi2K2pMYVl10EiQDCsWoB7VN84UR4Ne1UeDXtU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=7e96a109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目擊者稱，女子認為是司機故意不等她，因此一路狂追巴士。（微博影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201016/393608446853255168376904.jpeg/taRLjdRbCzVMUaHDcfCgcA4lcVQgEBRG80BOyfNATsk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201016%2F393608446853255168376904.jpeg%2FtaRLjdRbCzVMUaHDcfCgcA4lcVQgEBRG80BOyfNATsk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ba1b25a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事後巴士公司要求司機賠償女子1000元人民幣。（微博影片截圖）"},{"pid":"279f6521922a14f450f303208cf0c4127c68be6c","tid":2245410,"uid":204539,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:05:04.000Z","msg":"早知碌死佢算 慳返1000圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dccb0a506b56452cad3c643917036285ebc822d","tid":2245410,"uid":245441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:05:45.000Z","msg":"上次一爭執 司機扭軚將整架巴士衝落橋"},{"pid":"e0c5d6384259dc25ccfb746202dbef4fc0e212be","tid":2245410,"uid":1774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:05:57.000Z","msg":"兩隻生蕃"},{"pid":"14e8432d6484011e2ad1ce90008a98ad97f1baae","tid":2245410,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:06:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc7cbb397627242a53b1da7b7c3de80c8bc39e1","tid":2245410,"uid":178205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:06:18.000Z","msg":"臭雞陸狗po乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ecf6d9a3a384d798ddb18521fd49fb21746a1d","tid":2245410,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:06:36.000Z","msg":"低端人口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69616db512bb18dbabc9bcf9585d6b35a68c9e0c","tid":2245410,"uid":372227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:06:39.000Z","msg":"諗起05年蜘蛛俠第二集 仲有超能先生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37322c6434d3de1995e5a6fa269780fd4c3b96b3","tid":2245410,"uid":15084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"279f6521922a14f450f303208cf0c4127c68be6c","tid":2245410,"uid":204539,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"ci